WEBVTT

00:01:19.320 --> 00:01:20.000
Go on.

00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:22.480
Put on the gift I had custom-made for you,

00:01:22.480 --> 00:01:24.240
and fulfill our mission.

00:01:24.480 --> 00:01:26.720
This way, you won't betray my trust.

00:02:18.520 --> 00:02:19.250
The boss said

00:02:19.760 --> 00:02:21.440
you caused too much trouble this time,

00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:22.770
so he can't protect you.

00:02:23.160 --> 00:02:24.079
You have to figure it out yourself.

00:02:24.079 --> 00:02:24.960
Go hide somewhere.

00:02:24.960 --> 00:02:26.290
The farther the better.

00:02:28.240 --> 00:02:29.500
It's best to head south

00:02:29.800 --> 00:02:30.600
and go abroad.

00:02:34.160 --> 00:02:35.290
I've lived this long

00:02:35.400 --> 00:02:37.130
and never even left Jiangzhou.

00:02:37.360 --> 00:02:38.120
Go abroad?

00:02:38.680 --> 00:02:39.360
How?

00:02:39.920 --> 00:02:40.579
With money,

00:02:40.840 --> 00:02:41.970
you can go anywhere.

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:42.880
But your money

00:02:42.880 --> 00:02:43.600
is dirty.

00:02:43.720 --> 00:02:44.650
You can't use it.

00:02:52.480 --> 00:02:53.740
The boss gave you this.

00:02:53.960 --> 00:02:54.820
Take it for now.

00:02:55.760 --> 00:02:56.600
What is this little money

00:02:56.600 --> 00:02:57.440
going to do?

00:02:57.880 --> 00:02:58.920
Just take it.

00:02:59.280 --> 00:03:00.600
It's better than nothing.

00:03:00.600 --> 00:03:02.600
The boss has been good enough to you.

00:03:02.640 --> 00:03:03.480
Go hide.

00:03:04.600 --> 00:03:05.960
Wait until things cool down in a couple of years,

00:03:05.960 --> 00:03:06.820
then come back.

00:03:12.640 --> 00:03:13.500
Figured it out,

00:03:14.080 --> 00:03:15.080
and ready to talk?

00:03:20.040 --> 00:03:22.100
Sleeping here is too uncomfortable.

00:03:24.000 --> 00:03:24.960
The prison here

00:03:25.000 --> 00:03:25.930
is comfortable.

00:03:28.079 --> 00:03:29.610
I won't be sent there by you.

00:03:29.800 --> 00:03:31.079
I left home that night

00:03:31.079 --> 00:03:32.280
and went to Jiefang Road,

00:03:32.280 --> 00:03:33.400
near the old market.

00:03:33.400 --> 00:03:34.400
In the middle of the night,

00:03:34.400 --> 00:03:35.320
what were you doing there?

00:03:35.320 --> 00:03:36.240
Selling some ore.

00:03:36.240 --> 00:03:37.440
Jiaojiao is leaving.

00:03:37.640 --> 00:03:38.480
I wanted to make more money

00:03:38.480 --> 00:03:40.340
to prove I can give her a good life.

00:03:41.800 --> 00:03:43.930
But the boss there didn't even want it.

00:03:44.440 --> 00:03:45.770
Just this little thing,

00:03:45.880 --> 00:03:46.880
you kept it hidden

00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:48.200
and didn't tell us.

00:03:48.200 --> 00:03:49.730
How could I say such a thing?

00:03:49.880 --> 00:03:51.160
If my boss found out,

00:03:51.160 --> 00:03:53.220
how could I go back to work at the mine?

00:03:53.600 --> 00:03:54.730
You can go and check.

00:03:54.840 --> 00:03:56.440
That boss's surname is Chai.

00:03:56.600 --> 00:03:58.329
He's very famous in the market.

00:04:47.200 --> 00:04:47.720
Master.

00:04:49.480 --> 00:04:50.940
Chen Zhao is making a move.

00:05:11.200 --> 00:05:13.400
Chen Zhao started hanging out in society before finishing junior high.

00:05:13.400 --> 00:05:15.520
He became sworn brothers with a group of guys around his age.

00:05:15.520 --> 00:05:17.600
Even though he later joined Hao Weiguo's gang,

00:05:17.600 --> 00:05:19.480
he's still closest to these brothers.

00:05:19.480 --> 00:05:21.760
After we gathered this information last night,

00:05:21.760 --> 00:05:23.240
we immediately put these people under surveillance.

00:05:23.240 --> 00:05:24.960
We found them gathered here early in the morning.

00:05:24.960 --> 00:05:27.280
This cotton mill has been shut down for a long time.

00:05:27.280 --> 00:05:29.240
Chen Zhao's good brother named Dalong

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:30.360
is in charge of guarding it.

00:05:30.360 --> 00:05:32.159
They might be carrying weapons.

00:05:32.240 --> 00:05:34.080
Surveillance has tracked their current location.

00:05:34.080 --> 00:05:34.680
Here.

00:05:35.240 --> 00:05:36.240
Workshop No. 2.

00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:39.340
Come on.

00:05:39.440 --> 00:05:39.970
Let's go.

00:05:40.040 --> 00:05:41.280
Cheers.

00:05:44.120 --> 00:05:45.850
I'm leaving tomorrow morning.

00:05:46.159 --> 00:05:47.220
I'll miss you guys.

00:05:47.880 --> 00:05:48.760
All this way,

00:05:49.680 --> 00:05:51.280
we've come together.

00:05:51.800 --> 00:05:53.159
Through all the beatings

00:05:53.159 --> 00:05:54.040
and hardships,

00:05:54.560 --> 00:05:56.480
we've always been together.

00:05:56.880 --> 00:05:58.600
We are true brothers.

00:05:59.240 --> 00:05:59.840
Brothers.

00:05:59.960 --> 00:06:01.080
You guys take care.

00:06:01.280 --> 00:06:02.140
When I get back,

00:06:02.600 --> 00:06:03.730
I'll still need you.

00:06:03.960 --> 00:06:04.440
Come.

00:06:04.920 --> 00:06:05.960
Do well.

00:06:06.200 --> 00:06:07.000
Come, cheers.

00:06:08.360 --> 00:06:09.320
I'll assign the tasks.

00:06:09.320 --> 00:06:10.480
Listen up, everyone.

00:06:10.480 --> 00:06:11.960
Jia Peng and I will lead Team One

00:06:11.960 --> 00:06:13.560
to breach the main entrance.

00:06:23.800 --> 00:06:24.800
Teams Two and Three

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:26.330
will flank from both sides.

00:06:38.200 --> 00:06:39.120
Lin Xiao's Team Four

00:06:39.120 --> 00:06:40.159
will intercept at the back door.

00:06:40.159 --> 00:06:40.600
Captain Sun.

00:06:40.600 --> 00:06:41.080
Yan.

00:06:42.600 --> 00:06:43.440
You came just in time.

00:06:43.440 --> 00:06:43.840
Yan.

00:06:44.120 --> 00:06:45.000
You take Team Four

00:06:45.000 --> 00:06:45.920
and intercept them at the back door.

00:06:45.920 --> 00:06:46.360
Move.

00:06:57.280 --> 00:06:57.760
Zhao.

00:06:58.360 --> 00:06:59.480
Have enough money for the journey.

00:06:59.480 --> 00:07:00.840
It's a token of our appreciation.

00:07:00.840 --> 00:07:01.440
As for you,

00:07:02.240 --> 00:07:03.200
when you're out there,

00:07:03.200 --> 00:07:04.320
don't starve yourself.

00:07:04.320 --> 00:07:05.080
Make sure

00:07:05.400 --> 00:07:07.000
you keep your wits about you.

00:07:17.400 --> 00:07:18.880
Ah, keep it for yourselves.

00:07:18.880 --> 00:07:20.160
Hao already gave me some, really.

00:07:20.160 --> 00:07:21.000
Take it and spend it.

00:07:21.000 --> 00:07:22.040
What Hao gave you is his.

00:07:22.040 --> 00:07:22.880
This is ours.

00:07:22.880 --> 00:07:23.360
Right?

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:23.820
Take it.

00:07:24.240 --> 00:07:25.360
Just take it.

00:07:27.920 --> 00:07:29.380
Having brothers like you,

00:07:31.040 --> 00:07:31.840
it's worth it.

00:07:32.680 --> 00:07:33.080
Come on.

00:07:33.080 --> 00:07:33.720
Brothers for life.

00:07:33.720 --> 00:07:34.120
Drink.

00:07:34.520 --> 00:07:35.120
Police!

00:07:36.200 --> 00:07:36.840
Police!

00:07:37.000 --> 00:07:37.360
Go!

00:07:37.520 --> 00:07:38.080
Run!

00:07:44.880 --> 00:07:45.440
Stop!

00:07:45.840 --> 00:07:46.500
Don't move!

00:07:48.080 --> 00:07:48.740
Don't move!

00:07:49.520 --> 00:07:50.040
Stop!

00:07:51.320 --> 00:07:51.980
Don't move!

00:07:54.960 --> 00:07:55.880
Don't move!

00:07:57.320 --> 00:07:57.920
Don't run!

00:07:58.560 --> 00:07:59.159
Don't run!

00:07:59.840 --> 00:08:01.570
I'll shoot if you keep running!

00:08:18.040 --> 00:08:18.700
Don't move!

00:08:21.440 --> 00:08:22.440
Stop! Stop!

00:08:22.440 --> 00:08:23.120
Put your hands up!

00:08:23.120 --> 00:08:23.600
Stop!

00:08:25.200 --> 00:08:25.720
Stop!

00:08:25.720 --> 00:08:26.380
Don't move!

00:08:26.920 --> 00:08:27.480
Stop!

00:08:27.640 --> 00:08:28.240
Stop!

00:08:31.040 --> 00:08:31.520
Get up!

00:08:34.840 --> 00:08:35.440
Stop!

00:08:55.000 --> 00:08:55.840
Keep running!

00:08:55.960 --> 00:08:56.840
How dare you assault a police officer!

00:08:56.840 --> 00:08:57.960
I won't dare! I won't dare!

00:08:57.960 --> 00:08:58.600
It hurts!

00:09:01.760 --> 00:09:02.560
Take him away.

00:09:09.000 --> 00:09:09.530
Let's go.

00:09:09.760 --> 00:09:11.560
Your skills are pretty good now.

00:09:18.360 --> 00:09:19.360
Behave yourself.

00:09:22.560 --> 00:09:23.080
Go up.

00:09:25.760 --> 00:09:26.720
Is your arm okay?

00:09:27.000 --> 00:09:27.600
It's fine.

00:09:27.800 --> 00:09:28.400
Take him up.

00:09:28.400 --> 00:09:29.060
Be careful.

00:09:30.760 --> 00:09:32.120
Did you go check

00:09:32.120 --> 00:09:34.000
Ma Jinguang's alibi this morning?

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:35.680
I checked the roadside surveillance.

00:09:35.680 --> 00:09:37.840
He did go to the old market on Jiefang Road.

00:09:37.840 --> 00:09:39.000
He has an alibi.

00:09:40.720 --> 00:09:42.580
He's telling the truth this time.

00:09:42.960 --> 00:09:43.760
Look at this.

00:09:55.680 --> 00:09:56.940
It can be confirmed now

00:09:57.240 --> 00:09:58.640
that in Kong Jiao's case,

00:09:58.920 --> 00:10:01.360
Ma Jinguang didn't have time to commit the crime.

00:10:01.360 --> 00:10:01.880
Right?

00:10:20.600 --> 00:10:21.330
Ma Jinguang.

00:10:23.280 --> 00:10:24.120
That night,

00:10:24.560 --> 00:10:26.360
did you really go to sell the ore?

00:10:34.760 --> 00:10:36.960
I already told you I didn't kill my wife.

00:10:37.840 --> 00:10:39.440
When can I take Jiaojiao away

00:10:39.720 --> 00:10:40.780
and lay her to rest?

00:10:42.640 --> 00:10:44.170
When the situation allows,

00:10:44.360 --> 00:10:45.420
we will notify you.

00:10:45.800 --> 00:10:46.280
Yan Mi.

00:10:46.840 --> 00:10:48.300
That's a separate matter.

00:10:48.960 --> 00:10:51.440
I still hope you can find the killer as soon as possible

00:10:51.440 --> 00:10:52.770
to give my wife justice.

00:10:54.240 --> 00:10:55.280
When she was alive, she always said

00:10:55.280 --> 00:10:56.810
I never gave her a good life.

00:10:57.840 --> 00:10:58.840
Now she's dead.

00:11:00.000 --> 00:11:02.860
I don't want her to keep suffering in the afterlife.

00:11:14.120 --> 00:11:15.520
You've got a lot of nerve,

00:11:15.520 --> 00:11:17.180
assaulting a police officer.

00:11:17.240 --> 00:11:18.360
Hurry up and confess

00:11:18.360 --> 00:11:19.360
everything you've done.

00:11:19.360 --> 00:11:20.440
Think carefully.

00:11:20.800 --> 00:11:22.400
When it comes to sentencing,

00:11:22.400 --> 00:11:24.840
taking the initiative to confess and being forced to admit it

00:11:24.840 --> 00:11:26.300
are two different things.

00:11:29.360 --> 00:11:30.560
You won't say, right?

00:11:36.600 --> 00:11:37.330
Look at this.

00:11:37.360 --> 00:11:37.880
Look.

00:11:38.000 --> 00:11:38.730
What is this?

00:11:50.920 --> 00:11:52.560
I did plan to kill Zhang Biao,

00:11:53.160 --> 00:11:54.890
but I didn't kill him in the end.

00:11:55.160 --> 00:11:57.040
I hadn't planned how to kill him yet.

00:11:57.040 --> 00:11:57.900
He was blown up.

00:11:58.720 --> 00:11:59.360
Really.

00:12:05.520 --> 00:12:07.450
Why did you want to kill Zhang Biao?

00:12:07.720 --> 00:12:08.960
Who ordered you?

00:12:10.200 --> 00:12:10.600
You,

00:12:10.600 --> 00:12:12.320
how did you know I had someone behind me?

00:12:12.320 --> 00:12:14.160
Why do you have so much nonsense?

00:12:14.360 --> 00:12:16.090
Just answer what you are asked.

00:12:16.800 --> 00:12:18.240
Sister Jia asked me to do it.

00:12:18.240 --> 00:12:19.370
She gave me 200,000.

00:12:22.840 --> 00:12:24.500
The Sister Jia you mentioned,

00:12:24.520 --> 00:12:25.720
is Zhang Biao's wife,

00:12:25.920 --> 00:12:26.720
Wang Hongjia?

00:12:26.920 --> 00:12:27.400
Yes.

00:12:27.800 --> 00:12:29.040
When was the money given?

00:12:29.040 --> 00:12:29.640
How was it given?

00:12:29.640 --> 00:12:31.500
Of course, after Zhang Biao died.

00:12:31.760 --> 00:12:33.120
Although I didn't kill him,

00:12:33.120 --> 00:12:34.180
I thought about it,

00:12:35.320 --> 00:12:37.320
no one knew I didn't do it, right?

00:12:37.600 --> 00:12:38.760
I asked her for the money.

00:12:38.760 --> 00:12:39.620
And she gave it.

00:12:39.840 --> 00:12:41.000
Did she tell you

00:12:42.240 --> 00:12:44.080
why she wanted to kill Zhang Biao?

00:12:44.080 --> 00:12:45.360
Oh, officer,

00:12:45.520 --> 00:12:46.640
husbands killing wives,

00:12:46.640 --> 00:12:48.040
wives killing husbands,

00:12:48.080 --> 00:12:49.240
it's too common.

00:12:50.480 --> 00:12:51.480
I didn't ask much.

00:12:53.280 --> 00:12:54.600
As long as I get paid.

00:12:54.960 --> 00:12:55.720
Are you sure

00:12:55.920 --> 00:12:57.980
she only asked you to kill Zhang Biao?

00:13:01.600 --> 00:13:02.920
I guess so.

00:13:14.840 --> 00:13:16.360
Help!

00:13:16.480 --> 00:13:17.280
Help!

00:13:17.360 --> 00:13:18.400
You mean

00:13:18.680 --> 00:13:21.240
Wang Hongjia hired two people to kill Zhang Biao at the same time,

00:13:21.240 --> 00:13:23.360
and the other killer besides Chen Zhao

00:13:23.360 --> 00:13:24.200
is

00:13:24.200 --> 00:13:25.600
the real mastermind behind the bombing?

00:13:25.600 --> 00:13:26.600
It's just a guess.

00:13:27.280 --> 00:13:28.410
Even if Wang Hongjia

00:13:28.640 --> 00:13:31.600
might be the mastermind behind Zhang Biao's bombing,

00:13:31.600 --> 00:13:32.640
what about Qiao Sisi?

00:13:32.640 --> 00:13:33.440
And Kong Jiao?

00:13:33.560 --> 00:13:34.560
Why kill them?

00:13:34.560 --> 00:13:35.080
Master.

00:13:35.800 --> 00:13:36.320
Master.

00:13:37.320 --> 00:13:38.080
The bank confirmed that

00:13:38.080 --> 00:13:39.560
Wang Hongjia indeed, after the crime,

00:13:39.560 --> 00:13:40.760
withdrew 200,000 in cash.

00:13:40.760 --> 00:13:41.360
But

00:13:41.520 --> 00:13:43.320
her phone is unreachable again.

00:13:45.120 --> 00:13:45.880
I don't want to die.

00:13:45.880 --> 00:13:47.000
Please let me go.

00:13:47.000 --> 00:13:48.000
I don't want to die.

00:13:48.000 --> 00:13:48.640
Please.

00:13:49.160 --> 00:13:50.240
I don't want to die.

00:13:50.400 --> 00:13:51.680
I will give you whatever you want.

00:13:51.680 --> 00:13:52.240
I have money.

00:13:52.240 --> 00:13:53.280
I have a lot of money.

00:13:53.280 --> 00:13:54.540
I'll give it all to you.

00:13:56.080 --> 00:13:57.360
I won't say anything.

00:13:58.080 --> 00:13:58.680
No, no, no.

00:13:58.880 --> 00:14:00.320
Don't kill me.

00:16:22.920 --> 00:16:24.440
The house shows no abnormalities.

00:16:24.440 --> 00:16:25.770
No property is missing.

00:16:26.440 --> 00:16:28.300
If it weren't for this steel ball,

00:16:28.360 --> 00:16:30.090
we probably would have thought

00:16:31.480 --> 00:16:33.740
Wang Hongjia fled to escape punishment.

00:16:34.600 --> 00:16:35.160
Master.

00:16:35.800 --> 00:16:37.960
Zhang Biao's room is way too clean.

00:16:38.080 --> 00:16:40.340
I suspect they separated a long time ago.

00:16:41.480 --> 00:16:42.600
When we came in,

00:16:42.760 --> 00:16:43.800
the door was ajar.

00:16:44.680 --> 00:16:45.410
Steel balls.

00:16:45.520 --> 00:16:46.320
Bloodstains.

00:16:46.320 --> 00:16:47.050
Steel balls.

00:16:48.720 --> 00:16:50.720
Why would there be steel balls here?

00:16:51.880 --> 00:16:53.120
It must be connected

00:16:53.760 --> 00:16:55.020
to the previous cases.

00:16:55.200 --> 00:16:57.000
Maybe the killer wants to tell us

00:16:57.400 --> 00:16:58.400
that Wang Hongjia

00:16:58.560 --> 00:16:59.420
is in his hands.

00:17:00.520 --> 00:17:02.120
He might want to challenge us

00:17:02.920 --> 00:17:04.800
to see if we can save Wang Hongjia.

00:17:07.280 --> 00:17:08.010
Captain Sun.

00:17:08.599 --> 00:17:09.329
Captain Sun.

00:17:10.280 --> 00:17:10.760
Yan,

00:17:11.200 --> 00:17:12.560
I have some clues here.

00:17:13.000 --> 00:17:14.319
In Wang Hongjia's closet,

00:17:14.319 --> 00:17:15.579
I found two notebooks.

00:17:28.960 --> 00:17:29.820
Account books.

00:17:44.000 --> 00:17:44.640
Take them back to the station

00:17:44.640 --> 00:17:46.000
and have forensics check them thoroughly.

00:17:46.000 --> 00:17:46.360
Okay.